00:03:22,681 --> 00:03:25,946
<i>Oh, not even an hour a day.</i>

7
00:03:26,818 --> 00:03:28,877
<i>And...</i>

8
00:03:29,054 --> 00:03:33,114
<i>...how long has it been now,
since your loss?</i>

9
00:03:33,357 --> 00:03:35,848
<i>You're hoping I guess again,
aren't you?</i>

10
00:03:36,027 --> 00:03:37,585
<i>How long?</i>

11
00:03:38,062 --> 00:03:40,587
<i>Fourteen months, six days.</i>

12
00:03:40,765 --> 00:03:44,461
<i>I can tell you what time it was, down
to the hour and minute if you want.</i>

13
00:03:45,502 --> 00:03:47,231
<i>I can't help it.</i>

14
00:03:47,671 --> 00:03:51,004
<i>It's all right.
It's just a memory doing its job.</i>

15
00:04:15,463 --> 00:04:17,362
<i>- Hello?
- Hey, what are you doing?</i>

16
00:04:17,531 --> 00:04:21,194
I'm just running out the door. I'm late
for my appointment with Munce.

17
00:04:21,535 --> 00:04:24,698
Listen, I was thinking maybe
we could go out to dinner tonight.

18
00:04:24,871 --> 00:04:29,603
I don't know. I think I'd
rather stay home. I'm sorry.

19
00:04:29,775 --> 00:04:31,743
All right, well, that's fine.

20
00:04:31,911 --> 00:04:34,311
<i>I'll cook something fancy.</i>

21
00:04:34,513 --> 00:04:36,174
No, no, no.

22
00:04:36,349 --> 00:04:37,646
