23
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,878
No, I want to.

24
00:04:41,586 --> 00:04:43,816
Jim, I want to, okay?

25
00:04:47,158 --> 00:04:49,285
- Hey, Eliot.
- I miss you, sweetie.

26
00:04:49,461 --> 00:04:52,190
- Where have you been?
- I know. I haven't called.

27
00:04:52,363 --> 00:04:56,356
Don't be silly. I didn't mean it like that.
We haven't hung out in a while.

28
00:04:56,533 --> 00:05:00,469
- Give me a call, we'll do something.
- I'd love to. Bye.

29
00:05:09,212 --> 00:05:10,474
You need some help?

30
00:05:10,647 --> 00:05:13,740
I parked my car here.
Right here, last night.

31
00:05:13,915 --> 00:05:15,576
