69
00:07:34,244 --> 00:07:36,838
Sorry. Sorry.

70
00:07:37,247 --> 00:07:38,544
I'm sorry.

71
00:07:38,715 --> 00:07:41,979
Let me get the nice glasses
your mother gave us. Okay?

72
00:07:42,151 --> 00:07:44,847
- Speaking of psychotics.
- Yeah.

73
00:07:46,889 --> 00:07:49,722
What kind of a kids' book is it?

74
00:08:05,038 --> 00:08:06,733
What have you done, Jim?

75
00:08:07,107 --> 00:08:08,904
- What?
- What have you done?

76
00:08:09,075 --> 00:08:10,736
- Telly.
- Why'd you change the picture?

77
00:08:10,911 --> 00:08:14,004
- I didn't change anything.
- Think this helps? Taking him away?

78
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:16,510
- Calm down.
- I want the picture of the three of us.

79
00:08:16,682 --> 00:08:20,584
What did you think, that I
wouldn't notice? I wouldn't care?

80
00:08:59,154 --> 00:09:02,180
I come here hoping
to meet other swingers.

81
00:09:02,958 --> 00:09:04,186
You're the first one.

82
00:09:05,827 --> 00:09:09,194
We know each other. I'm Telly.

83
00:09:09,363 --> 00:09:13,766
Remember? Telly Paretta.
Sam's mom?

84
00:09:15,236 --> 00:09:18,569
We're all tired of condolences,
but I miss Lauren too.

85
00:09:22,642 --> 00:09:24,906
Well, I'm...

86
00:09:26,112 --> 00:09:29,980
I'm done for the night, so I gotta go.

87
00:09:30,149 --> 00:09:31,810
You don't remember me.

88
00:09:32,184 --> 00:09:36,314
- Sure. You want my swing?
- No.

89
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:40,422
Do you want to come home
with me?

90
00:09:40,592 --> 00:09:43,355
- Just live over there.
- Good night, Ash.

91
00:09:44,729 --> 00:09:46,060
You do know me.

92
00:09:48,032 --> 00:09:50,899
That's why you won't
come home with me.

93
00:10:28,002 --> 00:10:29,798
Jim.

94
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:36,470
Please don't ask me to let go.

95
00:10:38,645 --> 00:10:40,544
Jim.

96
00:10:53,959 --> 00:10:55,392
<i>Mom, look.</i>

97
00:11:04,268 --> 00:11:06,293
Hurry up, Mom.

98
00:11:14,310 --> 00:11:17,245
- There's your plane.
- Yeah, I know.

99
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:25,771
Sam.

100
00:13:09,949 --> 00:13:11,849
Jim Paretta, please.

101
00:13:13,419 --> 00:13:15,649
Yeah, I'll take the voice mail.

102
00:13:20,425 --> 00:13:21,949
I can't...

103
