I can't believe what you did
with the book and...

104
00:13:27,432 --> 00:13:30,400
And I was so good...

105
00:13:30,568 --> 00:13:35,232
...with the photos and the lock.

106
00:13:35,406 --> 00:13:37,840
You still...

107
