Please, oh, please.

110
00:14:08,736 --> 00:14:11,364
Please. Please.

111
00:14:52,242 --> 00:14:53,903
Telly?

112
00:14:55,279 --> 00:14:56,871
Telly.

113
00:15:02,652 --> 00:15:04,552
I can't...

114
00:15:06,122 --> 00:15:07,749
