There are photographs.

153
00:17:06,464 --> 00:17:09,126
People with your condition
look at a photo and see...

154
00:17:09,301 --> 00:17:12,270
...what their mind tells them to see.
You used to see Sam.

155
00:17:12,437 --> 00:17:14,996
- No. Sam took that picture.
- You're recovering.

156
00:17:15,172 --> 00:17:17,766
There was a woman.
We asked her to take a picture...

157
00:17:17,975 --> 00:17:21,672
...and that's the one that Jim took away.
We have a million photographs.

158
00:17:21,845 --> 00:17:24,404
No. No, he took the real book away!

159
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:26,514
Telly.

160
00:17:28,217 --> 00:17:31,948
Telly, I was hoping we could do this
without hospitalizing you.

161
00:17:42,397 --> 00:17:44,661
All right, all right.

162
00:17:45,801 --> 00:17:48,166
No, there... There...

163
00:17:48,336 --> 00:17:50,304
There are...

164
00:17:51,005 --> 00:17:54,304
There are photos that he didn't take.

165
00:17:55,609 --> 00:17:57,372
I'll show you.

166
00:17:57,545 --> 00:18:01,071
And we'll end this. We'll end this.

167
00:18:25,370 --> 00:18:26,769
Telly.

168
00:18:26,938 --> 00:18:28,906
Let's just sit down.

169
00:18:38,348 --> 00:18:39,815
Telly.

170
00:18:47,156 --> 00:18:48,453
Telly! Telly!

171
00:18:48,624 --> 00:18:52,287
Where are you going?
Where are you...? Telly!

172
00:19:11,311 --> 00:19:13,438
