Telly!

203
00:21:27,435 --> 00:21:28,959
Telly!

204
00:21:49,122 --> 00:21:50,350
<i>Who the hell is it?</i>

205
00:21:50,957 --> 00:21:54,289
It's Telly Paretta. Ash, please.

206
00:21:54,459 --> 00:21:56,086
<i>Are you gonna go away?</i>

207
00:21:56,261 --> 00:21:57,956
No.

208
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:07,269
Remember me?

209
00:22:08,139 --> 00:22:09,401
Yeah.

210
00:22:10,942 --> 00:22:12,910
Who am I?

211
