to drop Sam off or pick Lauren up.

231
00:23:34,551 --> 00:23:36,814
Can we talk about this after?

232
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:38,744
After what?

233
00:23:39,455 --> 00:23:41,514
After I sleep.

234
00:23:46,095 --> 00:23:48,722
